50|$|Another {{option is}} to use a rifled choke in a smooth-bore barrel, at least for {{shotguns}} having a removable choke tube. Rifled chokes are considerably less expensive than a rifled <b>shotgun</b> <b>barrel,</b> and a smooth-bore barrel paired with a rifled choke is often nearly as accurate as a rifled <b>shotgun</b> <b>barrel</b> dedicated for use with slugs. There are many options in selecting shotguns for use with slugs.|$|R
